metadata.name: DOS Larvas OG | Check
metadata.description:
Inspired by the checks movement created by Jack Butcher (@jackbutcher), we decided that a fun and creative way to make our mark within internet culture was to create this work with our own OG DOS Larvas.

The DOS Larvas used for this open edition were generated randomly using the same OG algorithm that we used when we minted them, almost one year ago.

Since then, the algorithm had been inactive until today...
